<p style="text-align:justify;"><span class="AddHand-editors">[A]</span>s for Religion they have none, but they all acknowledge a Supreme being, the Creator of all thi<span class="AddHand-editors">[ngs.]</span>  <span class="AddHand-editors">[T]</span>hey neither Adore, Worship, nor fear him, as they a<span class="AddHand-editors">[llow]</span> him to be all goodness, who does not Concerne hi<span class="AddHand-editors">[m]</span>self about poor Mortals, and of Course, is fro<span class="AddHand-editors">[m]</span> <span class="AddHand-editors">[himself]</span> goodness incapable of doing harme to any One.</p>
